Package com.vernalis.pdbconnector2.query

This package contains the classes for the PDB Connector Query definitions

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    QueryModel
    This interface defines a settings model for a PDB query.
    QueryPanel<T extends QueryModel>
    An interface for query dialog components which will contain a CountClearButtonBox.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    PdbStaticSchemaLoader
    This class loads the static schema held in the /json-config folder at the plugin root .
    RCSBQueryModel
    A class representing a full advanced query
    RCSBQueryRunner
    Class to run an RCSB Query.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    QueryResultType
    Enum representing the type of object to return as query execution result
    ScoringType
    The scoring algorithm to use.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    RCSBQueryRunner.QueryException
    An exception thrown during query executions
